    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in good condition and represents a solid, reliable used car that has been reasonably well maintained. The exterior presents nicely overall, though as expected with a used vehicle, there are some minor scratches and light wear marks consistent with normal use \u2014 nothing severe or structural. The paint retains good color and shine in most areas. The interior is clean and functional, showing moderate wear on high-contact surfaces like the driver's seat and steering wheel, but free of major stains or damage. Mechanically, the car runs well \u2014 the engine starts reliably, the transmission shifts smoothly, and no significant mechanical issues are present. All major systems including brakes, AC, heat, and electronics are in working order. This is a practical, dependable vehicle for everyday use that has been honestly represented. A pre-purchase inspection is welcome and encouraged.",
      "price": 35000.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 6
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is listed at $17,500, a price that honestly reflects its fair condition. The exterior shows noticeable wear \u2014 expect visible scratches, a few minor dents, and some areas where the paint has faded or lost its original luster. The body is structurally sound, but cosmetic imperfections are present and clearly visible. The interior has seen regular use: the upholstery shows wear on the seats and high-touch surfaces, and there may be minor staining or scuffing on trim pieces. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, though it is not without its quirks \u2014 some minor issues may be present that a buyer should be prepared to address. It has been maintained well enough to remain roadworthy, but it is not a pristine example. This is a practical, honest vehicle for a buyer who wants reliable transportation without paying a premium for cosmetic perfection. A pre-purchase inspection is welcome and encouraged.",
      "price": 17500.0,
